  "text_idx": {
    "en": {
      "title": "People in the oil queue are protesting",
      "author": "unknown",
      "body_lines": [
        "Aluthgama I.O.C. The people who were in queues protested today (4th) due to non-receipt of fuel at the gas station in 7 days.",
        "Due to the pressure of not getting fuel, the people in the queue of diesel and petrol vehicles parked on Galle road for several days, 2 km away from Aluthgama petrol station, up to Kaluwamodara bridge, protested."
      ],
